name: Any Percent%
description:
HEY YOU!  Yes, you. I have a question for you, how fast can you finish my game?

Any Percent% is a 3D first person platformer completely focused on being speedrun, how fast can you go through its 20 levels? Beat the game as fast as you can and post here on the comments or send to my twitter (link below) your best times!

Hi! My name is Mikel and I'm a videogame developer powered by coffee. I work proffesionally as a programmer and on my free time I do small projects like this one on my own. I hope you like this game and if you wanna talk to me or stay tuned on my next projects you can do it following me on my twitter page:

https://twitter.com/SrCoffeeMachine

Here I will post the 10 highest scores (with the name of the ones who achieved them) out of the people that post an image of their highscore either here in the comments or to my twitter. Good luck and congrats if you appear here!
